fanfic2ebook, An offline fanfiction reading tool, useful for archival and
generating ebooks for pocket reading devices.

Dependencies:
- Python 2.x (I forget which version but anything installed by default should do)
- LXML
- httplib2 (Optional but recommended. Provides HTTP caching and compression.)
- calibre (Optional. Only required for conversion to non-HTML formats.)

See the output of --help for usage instructions.
